public class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        if (n <= 0) {
            return false;
        }
        while (n % 2 == 0) {
            n = n / 2;
        }
        return n == 1;
    }
}
```

This solution works in the same way as the previous one, but it checks for divisibility by 2 instead of 3.

